{"type": "article", "id": 53316, "title": "一款厨房收纳盒，可以通过手机查看还剩多少东西｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-17T23:05:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 50355, "name": "KING JIM"}, {"id": 50356, "name": "Henge"}, {"id": 50357, "name": "Kamarq"}, {"id": 50358, "name": "Norse"}, {"id": 50359, "name": "Arper"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 109, "image": "img/article/article_show/201805172127330CdVEpxRJZDaF9i5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #026acb; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #026acb} span.s9 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #026acb; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #026acb} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Stok by Artifact Design</h3><p>亚特兰大设计工作室 Artifact 设计了一款名为 Stok 的厨房收纳盒。和很多厨房存储用品一样，Stok 也是透明瓶身，便于查看封装情况，也便于密封，以保持食物新鲜度。</p><p>但最值得一提的是，Stok 是一个智能存储罐，它配备了传感器来检测盒子的承载量。每个罐子都能与智能手机联通，显示存储量，也可以更好地帮助用户选择需要补充哪些食材，避免出现某种食材空瓶的状况。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212800BOgp7Rika2fX8HUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212800kMC2N7nQL19ERqd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212800XSvHDY1VywGe0tNc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212801AbhRlSKu9Q5YvnXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212801JYgxFfeMID438ZOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/05/17/grocery-shopping-is-so-last-summer/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kiik by Iwasaki Design Studio for Arper</h3><p>Arper 是一家充满活力、个性与创意的意大利家具公司。相比其他百年老店，Arper 公司虽年轻，但几乎所有产品在设计上均给人一种成熟和恰到好处的感觉。它以灵活的几何造型和流畅的线条为特色，并以此为基点，在色彩和外形上做出延伸。</p><p>最近，Iwasaki 设计工作室为其创作了 Kiik 系列，一个专为等待、休息时间打造的系列。座椅、桌子、沙发等均是模块化组合，可以满足候诊室、休息室、工作区，或是混合用途空间的各种需求。当然，你也可以通过组合，自己发现它的新功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018051721283992XKw7Wljhc5fCZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212839VNYGQfkFJP7hvjMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018051721283993EH87BoAx6P0wlZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212839nsgrFk4SpqXwR6Ca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212840RmznLkiZt2YwFur1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212840GlYRhJ3FyQaiZjXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.578323\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.stylepark.com/en/arper/kiik\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stylepark</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hacked IKEA Cabinets by Norse</h3><p>喜欢宜家的人都知道，以民主设计为宗旨的宜家产品，整体性价比相对高，但却有同一个问题：“太宜家了，大家买得都一样。”而有一群人，慢慢开始发挥想象力，对宜家产品进行大改造。他们被称为“宜家骇客”（Ikea Hacker）。</p><p>最近，又有一个纽约初创公司 Norse 玩起了 “IKEA HACK”。他们基于宜家的 7 款衣柜、电视柜和餐边柜，更新设计了饰面升级版的橱柜，每一款都以一位有影响力的女性的名字命名，包括美国前总统富兰克林·罗斯福的妻子 Eleanor，她也是一位外交官，以及黑人民权活动家 Rosa Parks 等在美国极具影响力的女性角色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212920xuRnEpIPtLk1cOK8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212920mkucWB1UC4fE3ZqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212921z3VRK9QPwZr8j1Hg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805172129216uORxQH0om3G5LpA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212921YfblApB8SzcXrd9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212921NpBJs0thMR236YxE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212923SKRVJXaZdTDejqQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/16/norse-ikea-hack-cabinets-beta-custom-design-womens-rights-activists/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Colourful Rentable Furniture by Kamarq</h3><p>在纽约，日本家具品牌 Kamarq 推出了一系列色彩丰富的家具。与传统家具不同的是，这是一系列只租不卖的家具，用户可以以月租的形式获得这个系列家具的使用权，租金从每月 5 美元至 18 美元不等，可以以半年租或年租的形式。</p><p>整个系列包括餐桌、咖啡桌、凳子、书架和收纳盒。它们的共同特点是设计灵活，可以以不同的方式使用，能够以色彩拼配的方式出现，也可以选择同色系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212955UkE5I2NudyqHBml7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778846\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212955mSNg9hYq3WE0Cal8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212956YoDmyJtuiXTwhz7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805172129587KzPs2aHVA30FmDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212958ymResNiAEf04n59o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212956EXAzVpC7gOsaftHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517212958sqy3lb2uG5ODSwRB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oxymoron Table by Massimo Castagna for Henge </h3><p>意大利高端家具品牌 Henge 制造了一张餐桌 Oxymoron，青铜制造的桌腿搭配一个手工制作的“微型马赛克”木制桌面，由 Henge 的艺术总监 Massimo Castagna 操刀设计。</p><p>桌面采用 Forest Fusion 的独特工艺制成，在手工切割核桃木和分层的过程中，产生一种大理石花纹，然后在顶部进行抛光，呈现出最终饰面效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213024M2qDSUy8uC5LicKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805172130247HuobmZ68kvLwG9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.422166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213024WVZp34vNRQO2IkBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213025tb1B6SIQuanXOhvJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805172130252t4RVrkQwE8qv5Gm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674883\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>pomera : Pocket Typewriter with E Ink by KING JIM</h3><p>日本公司 KING JIM 在众筹平台 Kickstrter 上推出了一款极简主义便携式电脑 Pomera。这款 Pomera 设备的外观复古，搭载全 QWERTY 键盘，单色屏幕以及令人印象深刻的电池续航能力，采用三折折叠设计，携带非常便捷。</p><p>Pomera 能够随身携带，随时记录你的灵感和创意。然后通过 QR 码或者 MicroSD 卡将文本传输到手机或者电脑上。Pomera 具备 6.0 英寸的 E-Ink 屏幕，两节 AA 电池能够支持使用 20 个小时。不过注意的是键盘采用日本布局，学习使用需要一段时间。售价 349 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2132003782/pomera-pocket-typewriter-with-e-ink#\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805172130523Fp6bql1eIn0DsVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213052FPXziADHWJrl3M6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213052tke94BQwW3UpRF80.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213053ukVrs2NCHTPWqlOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180517213053rMBwfxqZNi69T2s8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}